803
01:09:08,890 --> 01:09:11,390
[WHINING]

804
01:09:38,320 --> 01:09:39,950
[WHINES]

805
01:09:39,950 --> 01:09:41,020
[PANTING]

806
01:09:41,020 --> 01:09:46,660
[WHISPERING] Oh, God.
Okay, I know I said I'd never
ask you for anything again,

807
01:09:46,660 --> 01:09:48,990
but this time I really
mean it.

808
01:09:49,000 --> 01:09:51,540
Just leave me alone, please?

809
01:09:51,530 --> 01:09:53,560
Get outta here.

810
01:09:53,570 --> 01:09:55,930
[GROWLS SOFTLY]

811
01:10:04,050 --> 01:10:06,390
-MAN: Jeez.
-SEARCHER:
He's got a gun!

812
01:10:06,380 --> 01:10:08,380
MARTIN:
Police officer.

813
01:10:08,380 --> 01:10:11,180
[MARTIN CHOKING]

814
01:10:32,910 --> 01:10:35,820
[SIREN WAILING]

815
01:10:57,630 --> 01:11:00,360
What are ya doin', kid?
[SCREAMS]

816
01:11:01,200 --> 01:11:02,130
I was... I...

817
01:11:02,140 --> 01:11:07,550
They just shot the killer
over there. Get outta here.

818
01:11:14,150 --> 01:11:17,710
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

819
01:11:32,170 --> 01:11:35,680
Which one of you would
like to tell his wife?

820
01:11:49,480 --> 01:11:50,850
Michael?

821
01:11:52,150 --> 01:11:54,280
What's going on?

822
01:11:55,520 --> 01:11:58,350
Are... Are you okay?

823
01:12:16,740 --> 01:12:18,410
[ZAPPING]

824
01:12:18,410 --> 01:12:21,240
Shoot!
What happened?

825
01:12:21,250 --> 01:12:25,520
<i>You made it, Michael.</i>
<i>A bit clumsy, but you made it!</i>

826
01:12:25,520 --> 01:12:29,990
I killed somebody.
Again. I killed somebody.

827
01:12:29,990 --> 01:12:34,160
<i>Actually...</i>
<i>You were magnificent!</i>

828
01:12:34,160 --> 01:12:36,030
<i>The neighborhood</i>
<i>is covered in blood.</i>

829
01:12:36,030 --> 01:12:39,300
But you said
I wouldn't kill anybody.
You promised!

830
01:12:39,300 --> 01:12:43,200
<i>You protected yourself.</i>
<i>Your hand was forced.</i>
<i>You had no choice.</i>

831
01:12:43,200 --> 01:12:49,510
<i>Michael. Michael!</i>
[SCREAMING,
NAILS SCRAPING GLASS]

832
01:12:50,410 --> 01:12:53,680
<i>Now that I have</i>
<i>your attention...</i>

833
01:12:53,680 --> 01:12:55,580
[ZAPPING]

834
01:12:55,580 --> 01:12:57,350
Stop.

835
01:12:57,350 --> 01:13:00,480
This isn't a game anymore.

836
01:13:00,490 --> 01:13:03,090
This is crime. This is
just lots of crimes!

837
01:13:03,090 --> 01:13:06,320
<i>It's only a crime</i>
<i>if you get caught.</i>

838
01:13:06,330 --> 01:13:08,840
<i>There was a witness,</i>

839
01:13:08,830 --> 01:13:12,260
<i>and you know who she is.</i>

840
01:13:25,580 --> 01:13:27,680
No.

841
01:13:27,750 --> 01:13:30,410
<i>"Part Four."</i>

842
01:13:35,060 --> 01:13:37,200
[ZAPPING]

843
01:13:54,110 --> 01:13:57,540
Forensics says
you're gonna need this.

844
01:13:57,550 --> 01:14:02,050
And the Brower kid
is the one
who placed the call.

845
01:14:18,030 --> 01:14:23,130
[NAILS CLICKING ON GLASS]
<i>Talk to me.</i>

846
01:14:38,450 --> 01:14:40,580
What do you want from me?

847
01:14:40,590 --> 01:14:43,690
<i>You know who the witness is,</i>
<i>don't you?</i>

848
01:14:43,690 --> 01:14:47,290
<i>And you know</i>
<i>what has to be done.</i>

849
01:14:51,200 --> 01:14:53,930
<i>"Part Four."</i>

850
01:14:53,940 --> 01:14:56,610
That's it.

851
01:14:56,600 --> 01:15:00,170
I'm gonna go to Hayden
right now

852
01:15:00,170 --> 01:15:02,770
and turn myself in.

853
01:15:05,980 --> 01:15:08,440
[ZAPPING]

854
01:15:10,820 --> 01:15:14,320
You wanted the ultimate
experience in terror.

855
01:15:14,320 --> 01:15:16,020
Well, terror's in the doing.

856
01:15:16,020 --> 01:15:18,350
It's not watching horror films
like some child.

857
01:15:18,360 --> 01:15:23,430
And it's not spying on
Kimberly.
You get off on that, Michael.

858
01:15:23,430 --> 01:15:24,030
I love her.

859
01:15:24,030 --> 01:15:26,230
It could be any girl
in any window.

860
01:15:26,230 --> 01:15:27,660
I won't kill her!

861
01:15:27,670 --> 01:15:28,500
She'll tell!

862
01:15:28,500 --> 01:15:31,130
She won't tell!
She'll come to me first!

863
01:15:31,140 --> 01:15:32,100
Like last time?

864
01:15:32,110 --> 01:15:32,780
Stop this!

865
01:15:32,770 --> 01:15:37,510
Only you can stop this.
Her life or yours!

866
01:15:37,510 --> 01:15:39,110
Choose.

867
01:15:40,650 --> 01:15:43,380
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

868
01:15:44,720 --> 01:15:46,620
Cut.

869
01:15:46,950 --> 01:15:49,450
[ZAPPING]

870
01:16:05,940 --> 01:16:08,340
[DOORBELL RINGS]

871
01:16:14,080 --> 01:16:16,350
[RINGS]

872
01:16:19,450 --> 01:16:21,150
Michael?

873
01:16:22,320 --> 01:16:24,620
KIMBERLY: Michael?

874
01:16:24,630 --> 01:16:27,830
Michael,
are you home?

875
01:16:59,090 --> 01:17:01,960
-Igor?
-[BEEPS]
<i>Yes, Master.</i>

876
01:17:01,960 --> 01:17:04,260
Dial Brainscan.

877
01:17:05,230 --> 01:17:08,230
[DIALING]

878
01:17:09,700 --> 01:17:13,270
<i>Good-bye, Master.</i>

879
01:17:36,000 --> 01:17:39,410
[GRUNTING]

880
01:19:50,560 --> 01:19:53,830
What are you waiting for?

881
01:19:58,610 --> 01:20:00,880
Michael?

882
01:20:04,810 --> 01:20:06,840
Kill her.

883
01:20:06,850 --> 01:20:10,390
[EXHALES]
I can't.

884
01:20:10,380 --> 01:20:12,550
Cut her up.

885
01:20:15,790 --> 01:20:17,920
I'll do it myself.

886
01:20:18,330 --> 01:20:18,730
[GRUNTS]

887
01:20:18,730 --> 01:20:22,670
[LAUGHING]
Michael! You wouldn't
do this to me.

888
01:20:22,660 --> 01:20:29,060
-Who the hell are you?
-I can't believe you
still don't know.

889
01:20:29,640 --> 01:20:31,910
Michael.

890
01:20:33,910 --> 01:20:35,600
I'm you.

891
01:20:36,510 --> 01:20:37,910
No.

892
01:20:38,780 --> 01:20:41,410
[GASPS]

893
01:20:48,890 --> 01:20:52,590
[GASPS, GRUNTS]

894
01:20:56,430 --> 01:21:00,300
Ha-ha-ha!

895
01:21:02,800 --> 01:21:05,500
[SCREAMS]

896
01:21:11,410 --> 01:21:13,640
[GRUNTING, STRUGGLING]

897
01:21:20,390 --> 01:21:21,560
Michael.

898
01:21:21,560 --> 01:21:23,900
[ELECTRICITY CRACKLING]

899
01:21:24,460 --> 01:21:26,590
[SCREAMING]

900
01:21:26,590 --> 01:21:28,560
KIMBERLY: No!

901
01:21:28,560 --> 01:21:30,990
[CRUNCHING]

902
01:21:34,270 --> 01:21:37,770
[MICHAEL SCREAMING]

903
01:21:42,410 --> 01:21:45,170
[KIMBERLY SCREAMING]

904
01:21:48,820 --> 01:21:54,530
[SCREAMS]
Michael!
Oh! Michael.

905
01:21:55,290 --> 01:22:00,090
My God.
Michael, I'm so scared.

906
01:22:18,910 --> 01:22:22,810
Michael.
Please, you can't do this.

907
01:22:23,050 --> 01:22:25,810
Michael,
Michael, please.

908
01:22:26,450 --> 01:22:29,590
I don't care
what you've done.

909
01:22:32,690 --> 01:22:36,460
I love you. Please.

910
01:22:36,460 --> 01:22:41,160
[DISTORTED VOICE]
You'd do anything
to save your life.

911
01:22:41,570 --> 01:22:43,830
No, I love you.

912
01:22:43,840 --> 01:22:49,150
Believe me.
I just kept it a secret.
I never told anybody.

913
01:22:49,140 --> 01:22:52,540
[DISTORTED]
But that's over now.

914
01:22:54,150 --> 01:22:57,510
You watch me
from your window.

915
01:22:57,790 --> 01:22:59,160
I know you do.

916
01:22:59,150 --> 01:23:02,380
I've known for a long time.

917
01:23:03,020 --> 01:23:06,390
I watch you too.

918
01:23:06,560 --> 01:23:10,090
I bet you
didn't know that.

919
01:23:12,270 --> 01:23:17,910
Look, I take pictures.
Look. That's you.

920
01:23:17,910 --> 01:23:20,180
You, you.

921
01:23:27,510 --> 01:23:30,050
I love you, Michael.

922
01:23:39,060 --> 01:23:42,360
[BREATHING HEAVILY]

923
01:23:42,700 --> 01:23:45,370
[ZAPPING]

924
01:23:45,730 --> 01:23:48,530
I knew you couldn't
do it on your own.

925
01:23:48,540 --> 01:23:52,410
Game over.
You lose.

926
01:23:52,710 --> 01:23:54,550
Perhaps.

927
01:23:55,010 --> 01:23:57,670
But first...

928
01:24:01,050 --> 01:24:03,180
Surprise.

929
01:24:13,930 --> 01:24:16,000
Murderer.

930
01:24:24,140 --> 01:24:25,130
No!

931
01:24:25,140 --> 01:24:26,740
Murderer.

932
01:24:28,980 --> 01:24:31,380
No!

933
01:24:32,850 --> 01:24:35,720
No!

934
01:24:46,830 --> 01:24:52,000
[ZAPPING]
[SCREAMING]

935
01:24:55,470 --> 01:24:57,930
Oh, my God.

936
01:24:58,710 --> 01:25:03,480
What... The freaking hell?

937
01:25:07,050 --> 01:25:10,620
-What is this?
-[VOICE FROM BRAINSCAN]
<i>Hello, there.</i>

938
01:25:10,620 --> 01:25:13,330
<i>You've just experienced</i>
<i>Brainscan,</i>

939
01:25:13,320 --> 01:25:16,850
<i>the ultimate experience</i>
<i>in interactive terror.</i>

940
01:25:16,860 --> 01:25:19,600
<i>We're glad you decided</i>
<i>to play.</i>

941
01:25:19,590 --> 01:25:21,320
<i>Our special</i>
<i>state-of-the-art system</i>

942
01:25:21,330 --> 01:25:25,090
<i>releases a powerful</i>
<i>reality-enhancing signal.</i>

943
01:25:25,100 --> 01:25:30,370
<i>We here at Scientific</i>
<i>Perception Laboratories,</i>
<i>makers of Brainscan...</i>

944
01:25:30,370 --> 01:25:31,570
[VOICE CONTINUES INDISTINCT]

945
01:25:31,570 --> 01:25:32,300
It was a... A dream.

946
01:25:32,310 --> 01:25:34,180
<i>-...hope you've enjoyed</i>
<i>the feeling, however...</i>
-MICHAEL: A dream.

947
01:25:34,170 --> 01:25:40,410
<i>-We understand that reality</i>
<i>compression can be traumatic.</i>
-It wasn't even real!

948
01:25:40,410 --> 01:25:44,410
<i>-We offer these simple</i>
<i>relaxation techniques...</i>
-All right.

949
01:25:44,420 --> 01:25:47,180
<i>To calm you down.</i>

950
01:25:48,620 --> 01:25:52,050
<i>In a seated position,</i>
<i>place your head...</i>

951
01:25:52,060 --> 01:25:57,360
MICHAEL:
I didn't kill anybody.
There's no Trickster.

952
01:25:57,700 --> 01:25:59,390
<i>Breathe deeply...</i>

953
01:25:59,400 --> 01:26:00,900
Jerks!

